column4:
On §HOcean Worlds§!, §HAgriculture Districts§! are uncapped.
On §YWet§! worlds, £job_farmer£ §Y$job_farmer_plural$§! are replaced by £job_angler£ §Y$job_angler_plural$§! and £job_pearl_diver£ §Y$job_pearl_diver_plural$§!.
§Y$job_angler_plural$§! produce §Y8§! £food£ §Y$food$§! and §Y2§! £trade_value£ §Y$TRADE_VALUE$§!, and §Y$job_pearl_diver_plural$§! produce §Y6§! £consumer_goods£ §Y$consumer_goods$§! and §Y2§! £trade_value£ §Y$TRADE_VALUE$§!.
Adds the §H$trait_aquatic$§! trait.
column5:
บน §HOcean Worlds§!, §Hเขตเกษตรกรรม§! ไม่ได้ต่อยอด
บน §Yโลกเปียก§! £job_farmer£ §Y$job_farmer_plural$§! ถูกแทนที่ด้วย £job_angler£ §Y$job_angler_plural$§! และ £job_pearl_diver£ §Y$job_pearl_diver_plural$ __&3 9__.
